Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:48.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:52.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:55.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.65,0:26:01.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.53,0:26:03.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.87,0:26:08.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.42,0:26:12.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:21.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:25.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.89,0:26:31.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.61,0:26:36.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:39.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:43.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:49.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:53.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.84,0:26:56.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:48.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狀況完全不科學
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:52.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼貼畫般交織
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:55.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是誰在將誰呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.65,0:26:01.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回頭時感覺到你逃避的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.53,0:26:03.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}說這是錯覺未免無情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.87,0:26:08.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直覺該稱為才能才對
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.42,0:26:12.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我想瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}難道你並非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:21.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}現在就為你糾正青春的溫差
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:25.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解決 不如趁現在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.89,0:26:31.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解開你的懸疑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.61,0:26:36.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探尋少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:39.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:43.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引著我不斷沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:49.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨脹的好奇中分明不含心機
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:53.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人尋味
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.84,0:26:56.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這究竟是為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大家睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是明天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所謂全校盛事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要好好逛上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看 問答研是一點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將棋淘汰賽 沒什麼信心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 料理大賽絕對要關注啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天終於要開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自明天起的三天裡 請保佑我們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保佑我們度過那個難關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 迎戰文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:54.17,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1025,915)}大量積壓的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起得真早嘛 老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去參加文化祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是碰上什麼麻煩了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的傳統就是文化祭時一定會出麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別留下這種麻煩的傳統啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就給我個護身符啊 學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 那個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說聲謝謝就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 沒墨水了 而且筆尖開岔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把垃圾給別人啊 垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空的話我會去看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 別來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭開始了哦 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎你還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是挺開心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是社團活動歷史悠久的神山高中的文化祭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那不是摩耶花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是漫研的服裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花他們也是一看就一副過節的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也有什麼計畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是手工部部員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找她聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這衣服很襯你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你這是在COS什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別對正經打扮的人用這方面的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你那是什麼衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frol？Frolbericheri Frol嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.57,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：萩尾望都作品「有11個人！」中的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 之後還會戴上手套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那行李是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花要一直待在漫研嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為我是負責照看攤子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 別想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然發生了 那也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是文化祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聽說過 不過比想像的還盛大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱鬧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我說 弄好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯 弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大玩特玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去手工部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會馬上過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太介懷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果一直耿耿於懷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說里志 就連千反田都會跟著在意起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 折木同學 摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是努力就能解決的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有證據表明努力就能解決什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不努力就肯定什麼也解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是我買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說那話不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 是我下的訂單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本預定的數量是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上送到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二百本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的土星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 還沒開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我沒有確認印刷廠發來的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人都難免犯錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿成這樣真虧你說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用一個人承擔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿成這樣真虧你說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為部長 我也應該確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我也是交了原稿之後就沒再過問了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是古典部全體成員的失誤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我就是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你總算想通了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說穿成這樣真虧你說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 在開幕之前我們已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能盡可能賣出去 誰有什麼好點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一本多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經夠便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題在於古典部知名度太低 位置條件又太糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 大前提就是要提升知名度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及找個更好的位置擺攤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在別的地方賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我淨想著要怎麼把客人帶到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是顛覆性的想法啊 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 倒也算不上顛覆性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是開幕當天才說 能不能得到批准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行嗎 總務委員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種特權能不能獲得認可我也說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去找我們委員長或者學生會長問問怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總務委員長是誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹看看小冊子啊 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我倒希望你能注意到這個花招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 你不覺得很突出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 社團介紹的最後一個是古典部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我強行要求放在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小冊子是總務委員會編輯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是濫用職權吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想見委員長的話就到會議室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能由你去說情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這招倒也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我對談判沒什麼信心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由千反田同學去提 然後我在旁幫腔怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子她不是很樂意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 先不說這個 我想專注做宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才穿成這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有秘計呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以古典部的名義參加文化祭上舉辦的各種比賽和活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能獲得好成績 古典部的知名度也會提升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這想法真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不愧是福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點子不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方針就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田負責申請位置更好的攤點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志負責宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 折木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責看店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 這裡不能沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開幕式前的點名要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就按剛才的分工進行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡可能多賣一本是一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標 二百本「冰菓」完售！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}晝夜等長日 乃是秋分時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}從問答研開始怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}…似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第54屆KANYA祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉來轉去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是看這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體驗一下書法如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書法 來體驗一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs60\c&H0F0F0F&\b1\pos(1275,546)\3c&HFFFFFF&}良田方可出香米  千反田愛琉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話 請帶走留念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泉出築波嶺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.70,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：百人一首之十三 完整為「泉出築波嶺 飛落已成川 相思久長時 如淵無際深」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄然春光遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.28,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：百人一首之二 完整為「悄然春光遠 夏蟲忽已鳴 日下白衣曝 還看香具山」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此去因幡中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.45,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：百人一首之十六 完整為「此去因幡中 稻羽遍山松 嘗聞君相待 即歸如陣風」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來戰一局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柔光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.05,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：百人一首之三十三 完整為「柔光滿地傾 春日靜無音 何以心不寂 兀自亂紅櫻」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我是來找總務委員長田名邊學長的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是田名邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請增加古典部的攤點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Global Act  Global Act
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那個 我是古典部的部長千反田愛琉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您增加古典部的攤點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能聽你一句話就讓你們增加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是原則上如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什麼內情 就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商談的時候 福部同學應該是會幫忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 我一踩油門…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會出車禍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過每個社團都有自己的難處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能偏袒古典部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果請其他社團代售古典部的文集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不干涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是個好辦法 我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.36,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：河內COS的是侍魂系列的娜可露露 旁邊的女生COS初音未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河內學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連刀都準備了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過是塑料做的道具刀就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是武裝到鞋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 結果還不是穿COS裝來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前明明那麼反對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就聽河內的話不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.39,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：後面兩個女生分別COS巡音流歌和鏡音鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 湯淺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了不少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就買了條皮帶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 要是有收據的話就給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很難開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡代售「冰菓」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 這是誰的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？是Frol
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道「有11個人！」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我沒聽過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是以前的SF漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得是經典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次借我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你要借啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 各位 提起幹勁上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 已經開張了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看店…萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 先把一定能賣出去的部分寫下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到目前的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部成員就定為每人買兩本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上給顧問老師及保存用的 一定會少掉12本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就已經算很不錯了吧
