Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}誒 我都還沒喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那張紙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 朋克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的朋克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在賣文集的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全都要賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 因為有些內情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那給我一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 是客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得表現得熱情一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200日元一本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 根本沒在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我說你！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個能給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個啊 這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我是服裝研的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要舉辦時裝秀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻忘了準備正裝胸口口袋的飾物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個實在太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 真的要給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也是個垃圾 請拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們時裝秀的優先化妝券
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著這個到服裝室去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就會幫你做最好的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就里志會去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那傢伙也有他的堅持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之賣出去一本了
